    %h4 Woodblock Carving
    %p
      %strong April 12, 6:30 - 8:30pm
    %p
      In this hands on workshop by Purpose, you will learn how to carve a woodblock, deboss leather in a book press, and turn your creation into a piece of wall art. First, you will learn how to carve your own woodblock design. At a later date, to be determined in class, you will learn how to dye your leather. Then, you will attach it to wood with copper nails to make a piece of art.

    = partial(:"partials/_paypal-btn", :locals => {:id => "M6N8UHBHLVWJS", :price => 60})

