    %h4 Leather Ball Jar Wrap
    %p
      %strong April 14, 3:30 - 5:30pm
    %p In this hands on workshop by Purpose, you will learn to make a leather Ball Jar wrap. With your precut leather pieces, you will learn to edge dye, wax, burnish edges, chisel, and hand stitch.

    = partial(:"partials/_paypal-btn", :locals => {:id => "GM7Z83UV6GTSY", :price => 30})

