  .col-md-6.col-xs-12.work-shop
    = image_tag("bracelet-braided.jpg", class: "gallery img-responsive")
    %h4 Bracelet Class
    %p
      %strong April 28, 3:30-5:30
    %p
      In this hands on workshop by Purpose, you will learn to make two different bracelets to be worn together or give one as a gift.
      First, you will learn how to make a magic braid using latigo leather. For the second bracelet, you will be given pre-dyed vegetable tanned leather for you to personalize with metal stamps. Finally, you will be taught how to set your own snaps.

    = partial(:"partials/_paypal-btn", :locals => {:id => "2M6CRMP3ZYG56", :price => 40})

